In subsection ``Paradigm shifts ina  microworld'' in section 5 (p. 30 of MS):

"The answer xyy allows that the two strings are to be perceived in opposite alphabetic directions ...
but REFUSES TO GIVE UP THE IDEA that the strings have the same spatial direction; ...."


Probably metonymy: THINK-PRODUCT-FOR-THINKER??


